{"word":"G5362 - φίλανδρος - phílandros - fil'-an-dros - Love their husbands","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φίλανδρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phílandros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fil'-an-dros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Love their husbands</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"புருஷரிடத்தில் அன்புள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"loving her husband"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5384 - φίλος - phílos - fee'-los/5384\">G5384</a> and <a href=\"#/G435 - ἀνήρ - anḗr - an'-ayr/435\">G435</a>; <i>fond of man</i>, that is, <i>affectionate</i> as a wife: - love their husbands.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5362/5362\">G5362</a>, <a href=\"#/G5363/5363\">G5363</a>"}]}